&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>The conversations that you have in your head are the conversations you should be having out loud.&lt;/p>&lt;span class="cite">&lt;span>― &lt;/span>&lt;span>Unknown&lt;/span>&lt;cite>&lt;/cite>&lt;/span>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>The life you want is on the other side of a few hard conversations.&lt;/p>&lt;span class="cite">&lt;span>― &lt;/span>&lt;span>Alex Hormozi, &lt;/span>&lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/alexhormozi_the-life-you-want-is-on-the-other-side-of-activity-7105928499927891968-Pyry?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=member_desktop">&lt;cite>LinkedIn&lt;/cite>&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>The magic you’re looking for is in the work you’re avoiding.&lt;/p>&lt;span class="cite">&lt;span>― &lt;/span>&lt;span>Chris Williamson, &lt;/span>&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisWillx/status/1695783230514069790?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">&lt;cite>Twitter&lt;/cite>&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>And:&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>The magic you are looking for is still in the work you are avoiding.&lt;/p>&lt;span class="cite">&lt;span>― &lt;/span>&lt;span>Chris Williamson, &lt;/span>&lt;a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisWillx/status/1713540224620671063?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">&lt;cite>Twitter&lt;/cite>&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>Archives</title><link>https://www.jaredszajkowski.com/archives/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jaredszajkowski.com/archives/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Search</title><link>https://www.jaredszajkowski.com/search/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.jaredszajkowski.com/search/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>